name: POIJU.IO
tagline: POIJU.IO - plotter server for online or boat computer use
body:
### POIJU.IO

Welcome to POIJU.IO developer documentation. POIJU.IO is free service for nautical charts for Finland sea and lake areas.

### Want to use POIJU.IO?
Go to [www.poiju.io!](https://www.poiju.io) using a browser of your choice on laptop, desktop, mobile device or tablet. Remember to allow location services on your device.

Please follow POIJU.IO development and join the discussion in social media:
[Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/poiju.io/)

### Feedback?
Do you love POIJU.IO? Maybe you have some development suggestions? Please leave [feedback!](https://go.taplause.com/BkyuTguL)
